data.description: Sunset Broker’s open Sun, Jan 21, 3-5 pm. Pacific Heights' hidden gem- perfect fusion of nature and modern elegance. Home sits on half acre of privacy & spectacular ocean views. Each bedroom is a suite w/ full bath beautifully renovated. Huge family/media room/gym & awe-inspiring ocean views. Multi-generational living. Den has a separate entry and can be converted into a fourth bedroom. This haven features harmonious sense of tranquility surrounded by the vibrant colors of monsteras and tropical flowers. Renovations done 2020 - 2023 include luxury vinyl plank flooring, premium padded carpet, cherry cabinets, beaming backsplashes, gas stove, wainscotting bath walls, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, exquisitely-tiled baths, new sewer line, areas of new roofing, new water heater with copper plumbing, leaf-guard rain gutters, energy-efficient LED lighting, a terraced backyard, etc. The main level boasts of an open floor plan, and multiple lanais designed to maximize natural light to create a seamless flow from the large living room and dining areas to the kitchen. Dramatic rainbows, spectacular fireworks, & cotton candy skies off the lanais will leave you breathless.
